3. Shape uncertainty — they don't know which designs actually flatter their specific nail shape and length
4. Trend fatigue with the classic — they've had the standard white-tip French a dozen times and want something new but still polished
5. Screenshot anxiety — they save too many images and still don't know what to choose; they need someone to make the decision easier

